title: Cheesy Courgette-Haloumi Fritters & Avocado Salad with Cucumber & Lemon
description: Tonight’s salad spectacular is a texture-filled feast of crunchy cucumber and creamy avocado. The star of the show is easy to
spot - look no further than these crispy, crunchy, golden fritters, packed with halloumi and courgette, plus lemon and parsley for
a hit of zesty goodness!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
